                            <p>KGV's house system fosters identity, pride, and positive competition, promoting rapport between students and teachers, creating a supportive environment that enriches the school experience and strengthens the community.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://kgv.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/our_houses/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/4d6dec16dfe608b374f4b1eaaf32931a.jpg" alt="IMG_0020" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>STUDENT LEADERSHIP</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Student leaders shape KGV's culture, amplifying peer voices. They collaborate with administration to spearhead initiatives, foster school spirit, and address the needs of the entire community.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://kgv.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/student_leadership/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/24a0c999322b20f487a1ce6023307651.jpg" alt="Day 4 King George V School-203" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>SCHOOL EVENTS</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>KGV events celebrate the school's history, showcase student achievements, and deeply engage the community, fostering pride and belonging through music, art, and cherished traditions.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://kgv.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/community_service/">
                                    <span>Learn More</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                            </div>
            <div class="btns">
                <button class="prev"></button>
                <button class="next"></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            const ori_total = parseInt($('#section5').data('total'));
            let slider_loop = ori_total >= 3 ? true : false;
            $('#section5').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: slider_loop,
                dummySlide: slider_loop,
				afterSlide: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
					if(slider_loop) {
						if(current_page == ori_total) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2).Slider('start');
						}
						if(current_page == ori_total * 2 + 1) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1).Slider('start');
						}
					}
				},
                afterInit: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
                    if(slider_loop) {
                        slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1);
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">Testimonials</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="tabs">
                                    <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Students</button>
                                    <button class="tab" data-id="2">Parents</button>
