<p style="text-align: center;">Welcome to our campus! Join our Principal and student leaders for a short video tour of our facilities and learning environment. Click <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEXh46ZWngM">here </a>&nbsp;to watch!<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEXh46ZWngM"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/upload/page/43/self/69706bad9331b.png" alt="Self Photos / Files - tamn" width="500" height="282" /></a></p></article>
